E. Inhibin A Sample Buffer A:
One bottle, 10 mL, containing a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative. Store at 2-8°C until
expiration date.
*DSL-10-28100-4 contains one (1)-30 mL bottle.
F. Inhibin A Sample Buffer B:
One bottle, 10 mL, containing a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative. Store at 2-8°C until
expiration date.
*DSL-10-28100 (4-plate) contains one (1)-30 mL bottle.
G. Inhibin A Antibody-Enzyme Conjugate Concentrate:
One vial, containing 0.6 mL of a solution of anti-Inhibin α-subunit antibody conjugated to horseradish
peroxidase in a protein-based buffer with a non-mercury preservative. Dilute prior to use in Conjugate
